longBusinessSummary: Hawkeye Gold & Diamond Inc., a junior mineral exploration and development company, acquires, explores for, and develops natural resources in North America. The company explores for copper, gold, silver, zinc, and magnetite deposits. Its precious and base metals properties are located in the Golden Triangle of northwest BC. The company was founded in 1988 and is headquartered in Vancouver, Canada.
